    <dl class="eds-description-list-root">
        <div class="eds-description-list__item">
            <dt class="eds-description-list__term">Tax benefits</dt>
            <dd class="eds-description-list__description">
                If you are within the IRS income limits, you may be able to deduct all or part of your contributions from your federal taxes.
            </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="eds-description-list__item">
            <dt class="eds-description-list__term">Access to your money</dt>
