        | `.eds-description-list-root` | The `<dl>` element. | Defines the outermost container of the Description List. |


        ## CSS element classes
        | Class name                           | Applies to                                                                          | Description                                                     |
        | ------------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------- |
        | `.eds-description-list__item`        | A `<div>` element that is the immediate parent of the `<dt>` and `<dd>` elements.   | Defines a container for styling the `<dt>` and `<dd>` elements. |
        | `.eds-description-list__term`        | A `<dt>` element.                                                                   | Applies the desired typography and width to the term.           |
        | `.eds-description-list__description` | A `<dd>` element.                                                                   | Applies the desired typography and width to the description.    |


        ## CSS modifier classes
        | Class name                                         | Applies to                   | Outcome                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
        | -------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
        | `.eds-description-list--small`                     | `.eds-description-list-root` | Adjusts the style to render a "small" Description List.                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
        | `.eds-description-list--medium`                    | `.eds-description-list-root` | Adjusts the style to render a "medium" Description List.<br><br>_This is the default behavior if no other size modifier is present._                                                                                                                        |
        | `.eds-description-list--large`                     | `.eds-description-list-root` | Adjusts the style to render a "large" Description List.                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
        | `.eds-description-list--striped`                   | `.eds-description-list-root` | Gives the term/description pairs within the Description List alternating background colors.                                                                                                                                                                 |
        | `.eds-description-list--disable-border`            | `.eds-description-list-root` | Removes the borders between term/description pairs.                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
        | `.eds-description-list--inline-never`              | `.eds-description-list-root` | Adjusts the style to render term/description pairs in a stacked orientation.<br><br>_This is the default behavior if no other inline modifier is present._                                                                                                  |
